---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Our Story & Philosophy">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-warm-gray-900 mb-6">
          Crafting the Essential
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-warm-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Every great design begins with a simple question: What if we could make this better?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-warm-gray max-w-none">
        <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-sage-200 to-warm-gray-200 rounded-2xl mb-12 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-warm-gray-600 font-medium text-xl">Our Workshop</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-16">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-warm-gray-900 mb-6">Our Philosophy</h2>
            <p class="text-warm-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We believe that the objects we carry with us every day should be more than functionalâ€”they should be meaningful. Each piece in our collection represents hours of thoughtful design, careful material selection, and meticulous craftsmanship.
            </p>
            <p class="text-warm-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              In a world increasingly dominated by disposable goods, we choose to create products that are built to last, designed to age gracefully, and made to become trusted companions in your daily journey.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-gray-100 to-sage-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-warm-gray-800 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-warm-gray-600 font-medium">Quality First</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sage-50 rounded-2xl p-12 mb-16">
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-warm-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Commitments</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sage-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-warm-gray-900 mb-2">Lifetime Guarantee</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-gray-600 text-sm">We'll repair any manufacturing defects or normal wear, free of charge.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sage-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-warm-gray-900 mb-2">Sustainable Materials</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-gray-600 text-sm">Premium materials sourced responsibly, with respect for our planet.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sage-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-warm-gray-900 mb-2">Expert Craftsmanship</h3>
              <p class="text-warm-gray-600 text-sm">Every piece is made by skilled artisans who take pride in their work.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-warm-gray-900 mb-6">
            Ready to Experience the Difference?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-warm-gray-600 mb-8">
            Discover how thoughtful design can transform your daily experience.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/shop" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-warm-gray-900 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-warm-gray-800 transition-colors"
          >
            Explore Our Collection
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>